          {
            "_key": "span-1760818628396-ypy1mhicg",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "Aさんのように、看護師とのコミュニケーションに悩む看護助手は少なくありません。具体的な改善策としては、以下の点が挙げられます。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818628396-a3r94cqfo",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818628396-bbymazu8z-19bb61ef-60d1-494c-b1c6-f6b1a3e93605",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "* "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818628396-bbymazu8z-01ba98fc-909b-4afb-81a7-c24307b085e6",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "質問の仕方を工夫する:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818628396-bbymazu8z-a684d641-e54c-424f-a536-3b6c71de466e",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 曖昧な質問ではなく、具体的な状況を説明し、選択肢を示すことで、看護師も答えやすくなります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818628396-xl8wziort",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818628396-u6lqlns7l-3fcaeb21-ef4f-40d5-bc3b-150455a8c271",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "* "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818628396-u6lqlns7l-98cd952a-3fe7-49ce-b574-9a801fc80cb6",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "メモを取る習慣をつける:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818628396-u6lqlns7l-be33d148-bf1c-48ab-8697-e0d43ce25cb9",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 指示された内容をメモし、後で確認することで、認識の齟齬を防ぐことができます。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818628396-yxjkqju14",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818628396-n3dk5lh50-32cff398-84b7-4503-9299-3f623271582f",
